reviewText: I have searched for this for my husband for 2 years.  Thrilled that I found it.
A must for all Silver Screen Cowboy fans - Great tribute to the Sons and to the King and Queens of Cowboys
Best collection of factual information about Roy Rogers & Dale Evans with the Sons of the Pioneers 60 years of harmony live in concert 1994 on DVD and CD

I had purchased this Set in Branson MO!  If you want to remember Roy Rodgers and Dale Evans, and too "The Sons Of The Pioneers", you have got to buy this set of DVD and CDs.  One of the best Musical sets that I have ever purchased!!  It will bring a tear to your eyes, in happiness and celebration!  What more can I say!!!
